title: Winners and Losers in The Tech World
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin and deputy editor Alex Eule discuss the Nasdaq's comeback, the outlook for e-commerce and enterprise computing, the future of Meta, and wrecked IPOs.
